, ale ve správě komentářů \n*Použití produktu*.\n\nNicméně protože to bylo matoucí, i ve výsledcích vyhledávání na titulní stránce se nyní zobrazuje stejně.\n\nVe Správě komentářů ještě výsledek navrhneme.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://a.hsharp.software/rest/api/2/user?username=davidpodhola","name":"davidpodhola","key":"davidpodhola","emailAddress":"david.podhola@hsharp.software","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=48","24x24":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=24","16x16":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=16","32x32":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=32"},"displayName":"David Podhola","active":true,"timeZone":"Europe/Prague"},"created":"2017-05-26T05:56:56.713+0200","updated":"2017-05-26T05:56:56.713+0200"}],"maxResults":1,"total":1,"startAt":0},"resolution":{"self":"https://a.hsharp.software/rest/api/2/resolution/10000","id":"10000","description":"Work has been completed on this issue.","name":"Done"}}},{"expand":"operations,versionedRepresentations,editmeta,changelog,renderedFields","id":"10345","self":"https://a.hsharp.software/rest/api/2/issue/10345","key":"PDM-5","fields":{"summary":"Jak je to s pachtem p.č. 1888","description":null,"comment":{"comments":[{"self":"https://a.hsharp.software/rest/api/2/issue/10345/comment/10302","id":"10302","author":{"self":"https://a.hsharp.software/rest/api/2/user?username=davidpodhola","name":"davidpodhola","key":"davidpodhola","emailAddress":"david.podhola@hsharp.software","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=48","24x24":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=24","16x16":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=16","32x32":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=32"},"displayName":"David Podhola","active":true,"timeZone":"Europe/Prague"},"body":"Dobrý den,\r\n\r\nNa základě našeho telefonického rozhovoru si Váš dovoluji požádat o vyjádření k existenci pachtovní smlouvy na pozemku parcelní číslo 1888 v katastrálním území Chlístovice. Jedná se o pozemek na jižním okraji obce, podle ústního vyjádření místních na něm Vaše společnost v současné době pěstuje řepku. Pozemek nyní vlastní společnost BJP Company s.r.o, která jej zakoupila od p. Dany Čejkové.\r\n\r\nDíky moc za pomoc a pěkný den,\r\n\r\nDavid Podhola\r\n603 233 944\r\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://a.hsharp.software/rest/api/2/user?username=davidpodhola","name":"davidpodhola","key":"davidpodhola","emailAddress":"david.podhola@hsharp.software","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=48","24x24":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=24","16x16":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=16","32x32":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=32"},"displayName":"David Podhola","active":true,"timeZone":"Europe/Prague"},"created":"2017-07-24T09:11:30.760+0200","updated":"2017-07-24T09:11:30.760+0200"},{"self":"https://a.hsharp.software/rest/api/2/issue/10345/comment/10305","id":"10305","author":{"self":"https://a.hsharp.software/rest/api/2/user?username=davidpodhola","name":"davidpodhola","key":"davidpodhola","emailAddress":"david.podhola@hsharp.software","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=48","24x24":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=24","16x16":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=16","32x32":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc692ef2fe40956eedd6abca0de16352?d=mm&s=32"},"displayName":"David Podhola","active":true,"timeZone":"Europe/Prague"},"body":"Na základě telefonátu žádná